574
00:43:19,950 --> 00:43:23,220
♪So deep, so boundless♪

575
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:26,730
♪Just like your arms♪

576
00:43:27,220 --> 00:43:30,340
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

577
00:43:30,630 --> 00:43:34,270
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

578
00:43:34,270 --> 00:43:40,690
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

579
00:43:41,190 --> 00:43:45,590
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

580
00:43:46,050 --> 00:43:49,140
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

581
00:43:49,930 --> 00:43:54,730
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

582
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:58,840
♪I truly understand♪

583
00:43:59,330 --> 00:44:03,520
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

584
00:44:03,770 --> 00:44:09,740
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

585
00:44:10,246 --> 00:44:12,936
♪Using up all my fortune♪

586
00:44:12,940 --> 00:44:17,340
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

587
00:44:17,430 --> 00:44:19,650
♪Thank you for awakening♪

588
00:44:19,660 --> 00:44:24,740
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

589
00:44:24,880 --> 00:44:28,070
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

590
00:44:28,400 --> 00:44:31,930
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

591
00:44:32,010 --> 00:44:36,980
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

592
00:44:36,980 --> 00:44:40,970
♪No one can tear us apart♪

593
00:44:41,160 --> 00:44:44,510
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

594
00:44:44,770 --> 00:44:50,110
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

595
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:54,990
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

596
00:44:55,240 --> 00:44:58,640
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

597
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:03,290
♪No need to call out loudly♪

598
00:45:03,290 --> 00:45:05,960
♪No matter how much it takes♪

599
00:45:05,980 --> 00:45:10,390
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

600
00:45:10,390 --> 00:45:13,650
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

601
00:45:13,670 --> 00:45:17,720
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

602
00:45:17,720 --> 00:45:21,190
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

603
00:45:21,190 --> 00:45:24,960
♪Only by your side♪

604
00:45:24,970 --> 00:45:32,050
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
